results.name: sweet_snacks for spies
results.description:
Jimmy Debbie is a programmer, and he set up a server that repeats back whatever people send it. However, he is also rookie secret agent. He uses his server to dispatch codes for the spies he hired in the great pastry war. The spies enter a secret pastry passphrase, and the server sends them their code. It's very secretive. Sadly, the CEO of Oreos stole his old server binary and posted it online.

He can't seem to get the secret code, though. That's up to you!

The server is running at 104.236.113.247 on port 8888. The binary is attached as a file named sweet_snacks.
